Data persistence can be made through modules but will be very rarely used effectively, DB usage later



Templating engines : 
    - EJS (format : <p><%= name %></p>)
        - Normal HTML & plain JS in the template
    - Pug (replaces "normal HTML" with a minimal version) (format : p #{name})
        - Minimal HTML + custom template language
    - Handlebars (uses HTML, double curly braces) (format : <p> {{ name }} </p>)
        - Normal HTML + custom template language


EJS syntax : 
    <%= %> : display a variable
    <% %> : Use JS code